    <item>
      <title>日本结束负利率时代，几乎没有进一步加息的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-ends-massive-easing-program-with-first-rate-hike-since-2007</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行取消了全球最后一次负利率，结束了现代史上最激进的货币刺激计划，同时也表明金融状况目前将保持宽松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-ends-massive-easing-program-with-first-rate-hike-since-2007</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 03:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
